snippet.title: Johnny Depp arrives for the Black Mass premiere at TIFF - Daily Mail
snippet.description:
The 52-year-old looked notably different as he joined Amber Heard at the Toronto International Film Festival premiere of Black Mass on Monday, top left. In light of his new look, FEMAIL takes a look back at the transformation of the star, who  rose to global prominence in the 1980s on TV series 21 Jump Street. Clockwise L-R: Showing off his boyish good looks in 1987, 1990 and 2004, looking rugged in 2008, in Berlin in 2013 and looking somewhat different to his usual self on Monday.
